(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00953B-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、元大高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0056:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0056\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0056-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
